reviews.text: Best french toast. Nice tomato base. Coffee milk as expectedü yum enjoyed it.

In the shadow of closure because of property redevelopment, an old neighborhood restaurant gradually turns into a tourist trap. The environment may be too rudimentary for many and menu items are humdrum. It is, however, a trip down into the memory lane.

Very unique experience in here. Click the like button here if you were looking or the restroom and you had to intrude someone's living space, in the middle of their lunch, watching TV and the whole family starred right back at you like an intruder but you act casually, waived at them as you passed, wondering if you're at the right place at the right time. Yea just like in the movies but no one is chasing after you.

Fresh tomatoes soup base.

One good reason for people to go there, are because you could sit outside and smoke.
Cockroaches in my bowl of noodles. The owners are very chilled about this. Apparently they encounter this every day.

reviews.text: 茄牛撈旦麵正👍🏻
♡好味道二十年不變♡

之前上網睇好似話九月底會結業，一直都想試，終於可以試到。真係感覺好地道好舊香港嘅感覺 (餐廳環境相係後面) 🇭🇰 當初冇睇清楚係地庫行咗好耐都搵唔到，後來發現原來有條樓梯可以落。因為嗰個環境唔似有間餐廳，但係偏偏嗰度就係。😂
.
🍅 番茄牛肉麵 HK$37
佢嘅味道唔會好似平時罐頭，好濃好多溶嗰種感覺。佢係偏向比較鮮，而且冇咁鹹。
.
🧀 芝士蕃茄撈蛋麵 HK$42
個湯底係蕃茄撈蛋，再加埋成塊芝士，食起嚟真係好濃，成個芝士撈麵咁。

充滿懷舊風味，室內舒適一點，外面冷巷環境不會太受歡迎。 

試了蕃茄牛肉即食麵。 湯底鮮甜，不是外面一般濃郁的蕃茄味。 牛肉也鮮嫩可口，可惜份量有點少，是為美中不足。 凍咖啡 (特配少甜少奶) 亦完全不特出。

去試試吧，這種鬧市中的舊冰室買少見少了!
